publicwhip.spmotion: *S1M-841 Roseanna Cunningham: Census SSIs—That the Justice and Home Affairs Committee agrees to consider the draft Census (Scotland) Amendment Order 2000 and the Census (Scotland) Regulations 2000 at its meeting on 22 May, and that debate on the two instruments be limited to 30 minutes.
